title: Business insights and impact on the UK economy: 16 November 2023
content: This report discusses the impact of economic challenges and other events on UK businesses, based on responses from the voluntary fortnightly business survey (BICS). It covers aspects like financial performance, workforce, trade, and business resilience.

title: Financial Performance - Business insights and impact on the UK economy
content: This section of the report explores how trading businesses' turnover in October 2023 compared with September 2023, excluding seasonal trading.
